                                   <p style="text-align:justify"> The bureau is made up of the following Departments: Land Services, deeds and planning research and statistics</p>
                       <ol>
                           <li> <p><strong>Deeds Department</strong></p>
                               <p style="text-align:justify"> The deeds department is saddled with the responsibility of issuing title certificate for private owned land. Deed Registry is a section under the deeds department. 
                                It deals with the section of all completed deeds or instrument and grants upon request certified true copy of registered instruments. It conducts searches to reveal the status of registered instrument for the public.</p>
			               </li>
                           <li><p><strong>Land Services Department</strong></p>
                                <p> The land services department has the following sections:</p>
                   
                                
                                   <p>•	Valuation and Housing: The section is in charge of all valuation requests from the ministry department and government agencies. It manages rural housing estates and government building within and outside the state.</p> 
                               
                              
                                    <p>•	Acquisition and Compensation: The section deals with Valuation for compulsory acquisitions and purchases in the state. It also ideals with all derequisition matters and Processes compensation claims in respect of federal state and local government.</p>
                              
                              
                                    <p>•	Development And Management: The section deals with the management of all government estates throughout the state. It deals with the provision of infrastructural facilities within the estates. It processes applications for direct, grants on residential, commercial and industrial estates.</p>
                               
                             
                                    <p>•	Planning Research And Statistics: The section deals with initiation of policies on land use and management matters. They are involved in compilation of information for computerization purposes. They also conduct research into modern land management techniques and ICT deployment in land matters.
                                    They also help facilitate stake holders meeting and see to the capacity building for staff.</p>
                                
                           </li>
