                           <p style="text-align:justify">Geographic Information Services develops, maintains and
                        distributes the State’s primary geographic information including the Ondo State’s Coordinate Reference System, the Ondo State Address File, the Ondo State Property Records Database, and the Ondo State Aerial Photography Collection.</p>
